('story_thread_001', 'proj_teamsync_001', 'User Story: User replies in thread', 'As a user, I want to reply to a specific message in a thread so that my response is connected to the original message. Acceptance: Thread view shows context, replies visible, nested organization.', 'user_stories', 'user_story', 'done', 'critical', 'Ryan O''Connor', 'feat_thread_001', '{"epic": "threads", "story_points": 4}', 1, NOW() - INTERVAL '110 days', NOW() - INTERVAL '35 days'),
