('story_voice_001', 'proj_teamsync_001', 'User Story: User initiates video call', 'As a user, I want to start a video call with a colleague so that I can communicate face-to-face. Acceptance: Click to call, notification sent, auto-accept option, call timer.', 'user_stories', 'user_story', 'in_progress', 'critical', 'Aisha Williams', 'req_voice_001', '{"epic": "voice_video", "story_points": 5}', 1, NOW() - INTERVAL '110 days', NOW() - INTERVAL '35 days'),
